# ACFE Shop — Dashboard UI Style

Reference: light admin dashboard (Fily-style). Apply to all staff-facing UI (memos, inventory, waste, sales).

## Layout

- Page background: light gray (`#f4f7f6` or `gray-50`).
- Content in **white cards**: rounded (`rounded-lg`, ~8px), subtle shadow (`shadow-sm`), generous padding (`p-4`–`p-6`).
- **Top bar**: logo/app name left, search center or wide, utilities right (notifications, profile dropdown).
- **Secondary nav**: horizontal tabs/links with small line icons below the header.
- Grid: KPI row → summary badges → 2–3 column mid section → full-width data table.

## Color & status

| Role | Use | Example |
|------|-----|---------|
| Success / growth | KPI up, “Progress” | emerald/green |
| Info / primary action | Import, Update, links | blue (`#3b82f6` range) |
| Warning / pending | “Open”, alerts | amber/orange |
| Danger / on hold | errors, blocked | soft red/rose |

Status in tables: **pill badges** (rounded-full, small text), not plain text.

## Typography & density

- Sans-serif system stack (Inter, system-ui).
- Hierarchy: bold large numbers on KPIs; `text-sm text-gray-500` for labels and secondary copy.
- Breathable spacing between cards (`gap-4`–`gap-6`); avoid cramped tables.

## Components to reuse

- **KPI cards**: metric + % change + mini sparkline or donut.
- **Summary badges**: colored rounded blocks (icon + amount + “This month”).
- **Charts**: line (trends), bar (monthly), donut (distribution)—muted grid, clear legend.
- **Tables**: alternating row tint, avatar initials in circles, right-aligned actions.
- **Buttons**: primary = solid blue; secondary = outline or text-only (“View more”).

## Data viz for acfe_shop

Map modules to this pattern: sales → revenue KPIs + charts; inventory → stock levels + low-par alerts; waste → cost % + trend; memos → feed/timeline instead of generic tickets.

Do **not** default to dark mode or heavy gradients unless the user asks.
